'''Chral''' was a [[Gambling/Legends|gambler]] who was found on the ''[[Ananuru Express]]'' when it was auctioning a secret [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Imperial]] brainwashing virus. He, along with [[Jemmy]] and [[Tol (gambler)|Tol]], knew nothing about the auction and were just there to win money from rich people. He was pleasant and amiable and when a fight broke out he simply stayed under cover.

